title: Haier Refrigerator Upper Freezer Basket
description: Haier Refrigerator Upper Freezer Basket ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 16 Reviews PartSelect Number PS2356327 Manufacturer Part Number WR21X10208 The freezer basket helps organize food in the freezer easier. The basket measures approximately 7 1/2” high by 16.75” deep. The freezer basket is white in color and made of metal. This is a genuine OEM part and is sold individually.

installationInstructions.title: Ordered additional baskets for my new freezer.
installationInstructions.content: Ordered two baskets, arrived in two separate shipments two days apart. Both baskets wrong size for freezer. Information sent to customer service and haven't heard anything back.
